'''''Birja''''' is a popular  [[Azerbaijan]]i weekly free-of-charge [[newspaper]]  for announcements and [[classified advertising]] published by the Birja VDV. It was founded by Rafiq Abasov.{{citation needed|date=January 2017}} The newspaper has one of the widest [[newspaper circulation|circulation]] in [[Azerbaijan]] (averaging over 10,000 copies every week).{{citation needed|date=January 2017}}

''Birja'' was founded in 1992 with the goal of providing an advertising newspaper in the Azerbaijan market, where generally only a single local ad newspaper was available.

''Birja'' supports a nationwide project of [[Khinalug]] village.{{citation needed|date=January 2017}}

